    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Lightweight, short jackets that are zipped up the front, sometimes with closefitting waistband and cuffs to protect against the wind. These are worn as sports and leisure wear.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
